{"id": "art-590", "label": "Art. 590", "title": "Art. 590: Obligaţiile condamnatului în cazul amânării executării", "slug": "art-590", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1475081829\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1076\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1475081829\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 590:\nObliga&#355;iile condamnatului în cazul amân&#259;rii execut&#259;rii </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1343276605\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1075\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1343276605\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Pe durata\namân&#259;rii execut&#259;rii pedepsei, condamnatul trebuie s&#259; respecte\nurm&#259;toarele obliga&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1897065379\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1074\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1897065379\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)s&#259; nu dep&#259;&#351;easc&#259; limita\nteritorial&#259; fixat&#259; decât în condi&#355;iile stabilite de\ninstan&#355;&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2247708\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1073\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2247708\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)s&#259; ia leg&#259;tura, în termenul stabilit de\ninstan&#355;&#259;, cu organul de poli&#355;ie desemnat de aceasta în cuprinsul\nhot&#259;rârii de amânare a execut&#259;rii pedepsei închisorii pentru a fi\nluat în eviden&#355;&#259; &#351;i a stabili mijlocul de comunicare\npermanent&#259; cu organul de supraveghere, precum &#351;i s&#259; se prezinte\nla instan&#355;&#259; ori de câte ori este chemat;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_127215522\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1072\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_127215522\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)s&#259; nu î&#351;i schimbe locuin&#355;a f&#259;r&#259;\ninformarea prealabil&#259; a instan&#355;ei care a dispus amânarea;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_525121410\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1071\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_525121410\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)s&#259; nu de&#355;in&#259;, s&#259; nu foloseasc&#259;\n&#351;i s&#259; nu poarte nicio categorie de arme;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2023290177\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1070\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2023290177\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)pentru cazul prev&#259;zut la art. 589 alin. (1) lit. a),\ns&#259; se prezinte de îndat&#259; la unitatea sanitar&#259; la care\nurmeaz&#259; s&#259; fac&#259; tratamentul, iar pentru cazul prev&#259;zut la\nart. 589 alin. (1) lit. b), s&#259; îngrijeasc&#259; copilul mai mic de un an.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_989312426\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1069\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_989312426\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Pe durata\namân&#259;rii execut&#259;rii pedepsei, instan&#355;a poate impune\ncondamnatului s&#259; respecte una sau mai multe dintre urm&#259;toarele\nobliga&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_271132644\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1068\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_271132644\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)s&#259; nu se afle în anumite locuri sau la anumite\nmanifest&#259;ri sportive, culturale ori la alte adun&#259;ri publice,\nstabilite de instan&#355;&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_734905654\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1067\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_734905654\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)s&#259; nu comunice cu persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259;\nsau cu membri de familie ai acesteia, cu persoanele cu care a comis\ninfrac&#355;iunea sau cu alte persoane, stabilite de instan&#355;&#259;, ori\ns&#259; nu se apropie de acestea;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1368701755\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1066\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1368701755\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)s&#259; nu conduc&#259; niciun vehicul sau anumite\nvehicule stabilite.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1830544011\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1065\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1830544011\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)abrogat</span></p>"}